Title: Tango
Plot: A high school party turns tragic when a teenager is found dead, and the detectives end up playing games with the two leading suspects to find out the real story. Unfortunately, unwanted attention from a juror for A.D.A. Rubirosa may disrupt the trial.
GuestStars: Jeffrey DeMunn, Maria Dizzia, Molly Ephraim, Pedro Pascal, Lisa Joyce, Scott William Winters, Nestor Serrano, Marlyne Afflack, Kathleen Garrett
